Class ListMap

java.lang.Object
  ListMap

public class ListMap
extends java.lang.Object

ListMap implements a simple Map data structure. The implementation is based on a doubly-linked list and consequently suitable only for small maps as run-time of basic operation is linear in number of entries.

Version:
March 15th 2013
Author:
Bill Keller
